### Fazer login para obter token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "casamento123"
}

### Variável para armazenar o token (substitua pelo token obtido no login)
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

### ========== ROTAS ADMINISTRATIVAS DE PRESENTES ==========

### Listar todos os presentes (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/gifts/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar presentes ordenados por preço (crescente)
GET http://localhost:3000/gifts/admin?sortByPrice=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar apenas presentes comprados
GET http://localhost:3000/gifts/admin?purchased=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar apenas presentes disponíveis
GET http://localhost:3000/gifts/admin?purchased=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar novo presente
POST http://localhost:3000/gifts/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Conjunto de Taças de Cristal",
  "description": "Conjunto com 6 taças de cristal para vinho tinto",
  "price": 189.90,
  "image": "https://example.com/tacas.jpg"
}

### Buscar presente por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/gifts/admin/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar presente
PUT http://localhost:3000/gifts/admin/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Conjunto de Taças de Cristal Premium",
  "price": 229.90,
  "purchased": false
}

### Marcar presente como comprado
PUT http://localhost:3000/gifts/admin/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purchased": true
}

### Deletar presente
DELETE http://localhost:3000/gifts/admin/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Estatísticas dos presentes
GET http://localhost:3000/gifts/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

